					<h4>LML: A chance to prove itself</h4>
				</div>

				<div class="section-body">
					<p>Now that we have a better idea of what the Scorpion is capable of, it's time to move on and give the GM crowd
					some love. We've seen a lot of posts on our <a href="https://www.facebook.com/hsperformance?fref=ts" target="_blank">Facebook</a> page and heard <a href="http://www.hsperformance.com/1/" target="_blank">endless chatter</a> about the LML far out-performing
					the Scorpion. Is all the talk legit? I guess we'll see. We don't really care who 'wins', we just need to see what the Duramax can do.</p>
					<%= link_to "Get the specs on our LML Duramax 6.6L", new_user_registration_path, :class => "btn btn-success" %>
